      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Falconer%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Chadakoin River, the outlet of Chautauqua Lake, winds through Falconer before joining Cassadaga Creek at Levant.",
